Package todoapplication.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CategoryFilter
    A class representing a filter that filters a Collection of ToDos by category.
    CollectionOfToDos
    A class representing a collection of ToDos.
    CompletionFilter
    A class representing a filter that filters a Collection of ToDos by completion status.
    CSVFileReader
    A class representing a CSV Reader.
    CSVProcessor
    The CSV file processor class.
    DateSorter
    A class that implements functionality to sort a collection of ToDos.
    PrioritySorter
    A class that implements functionality to sort a collection of ToDos.
    Processor
    Main Model Class : Processor.
    ToDo
    A class representing a Todo.
    ToDo.ToDoBuilder
    A static class representing a Builder to construct ToDo objects
    ToDoCreator
    A ToDo Creator class that has two methods, one to create a ToDo from a line in a CSV file and another method to create a new ToDo with the specified fields.
    ToDoListToCSVWriter
    A class representing a Writer that takes a list of ToDos and writes a CSV files displaying the ToDo information.
    ToDoUpdater
    A class representing a ToDo Updater.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FileErrorException
    Custom Exception thrown if the code encounters a CSV file without data
    IDNotFoundException
    A class representing the checked exception that occurs when a given ID is not found in the Collection
